spirit:component.spirit:name: cont_microblaze_axi_timebase_wdt_0_0
spirit:component.spirit:description: The Advanced eXtensible Lite (AXI) Timebase Watchdog Timer is a 32-bit peripheral that provides a 32-bit free-running timebase and watchdog timer.

spirit:parameter.spirit:name: C_WDT_INTERVAL
spirit:parameter.spirit:description: Indicates the exponent for setting the length of the WDT interval. WDT interval = (2^C_WDT_INTERVAL) x Tclk
